<seg id="1405">I don’t think any budgets are 100 percent accurate.</seg>
<seg id="1406">What I mentioned earlier, the permanent salaries, the casual wages, overtime, agency nurses, if I add them all up, I think what we have tried to do and which is the reason for asking for this $8.6 million is it’s our best estimate in terms of how much will be covered under the compensation and benefits. I think that’s the closest that we can get it.</seg>
