<seg id="7">"I am unsure when he acquired this picture, or who J.H. is (noted on the back of the photo), but I do know he had a lot of connections in the North."</seg>
<seg id="8">"I do realize this photo is from a long time ago, but perhaps someone recognizes someone … and perhaps this is a photo of someone’s family and they would like it returned."</seg>
<seg id="9">"Most sincerely,"</seg>
<seg id="10">Sarah Howard</seg>
